		<title>01GENERAL DESCRIPTION OF AREA</title>
		<content> THIS IS A SPARSELY POPULATED RURAL    
 AREA CLOSE TO THE SMALL MARKET TOWN OF
 ABERGAVENNY WHICH PROVIDES THE        
 FOLLOWING AMENITIES:-                 
 SHOPS, SPORTS FACILITIES, MEDICAL     
 SERVICES, HOTELS, AMATEUR THEATRE,    
 CINEMA, ETC.                          
                                       
 THE SKY-LINE TO THE WEST OF THE AREA  
 IS DOMINATED BY THE SKIRRID FAWR,     
 SUGAR LOAF AND BLORENGE MOUNTAINS.    
                                       
 APART FROM FARMING AND HORTICULTURE,  
 EMPLOYMENT IS ONLY AVAILABLE OUTSIDE  
 THE AREA.                             
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
